    //     total = dist[1][i][j] + dist[2][i][j] + dist[3][i][j] 
    //     but if (i,j) is already an X of some component, the dist for that component is 0.
    // (B) Connect component A to B via one path, and B to C via another path.
    //     This is equivalent to: dist[1][i][j] + dist[2][i][j] + dist[2][p][q] + dist[3][p][q] over two cells.
    //     But this is covered by case (A) if we pick the right meeting cell(s) — actually not always:
